{
  "stem": "11290.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this was one of the sensational things that I remember, seeing that fat guy sitting there with all the young boys.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the same man, a few months later, was dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Also, he was one of the founders of the most faithful, early adherence of Hitler.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also an encounter in 1933, in the very early days when the Nazis had just gotten into power and had just made laws that-- they were-- they were extremely occupied with sex.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had-- you could feel that that was a very important thing, the, the fear of the fact that-- the fear or the envy-- I don't know what it was-- that Jews could contaminate the German race.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a day in which I had a-- I took a date with me to a cafe near Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that cafe was outside on a little mountain on a very steep hill.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was driving my father's car and was very concerned about the car.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wouldn't want it-- better bring it home in good condition.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after I made my way up this rocky road with the girl in the car, I saw when I got up there all these black Mercedes cars, perhaps five or six of them, that were trademarks of Nazi leadership.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I thought to myself, I should not stay, but to turn around now-- and it was so steep.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't know how to turn around, so I, I didn't want to say anything to the girl.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we went ahead and we sat down, and we ordered a little supper.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
